column2: SELECT TOP # s.apogee_id, s.ra, s.dec, s.glon, s.glat, s.vhelio_avg, s.vscatter, s.vhelio_avg, a.fe_h, a.mg_fe, a.teff, a.logg, a.m_h, a.alpha_m, dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlagN(a.aspcapflag), dbo.fApogeeStarFlagN(s.starflag) FROM apogeeStar s JOIN aspcapStar a on a.apstar_id = s.apstar_id WHERE (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and  (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and (a.aspcapflag & dbo.fApogeeAspcapFlag(&&&)) = # and (s.starflag & dbo.fApogeeStarFlag(&&&)) = # and (s.starflag & dbo.fApogeeStarFlag(&&&)) = # and  s.vscatter < # and s.vscatter > # and a.mg_fe ># and a.mg_fe < # and a.logg >#
